Why should I participate in Code2Create?

Code2Create is one of the biggest college-level hackathons in the country and promises to be a great learning experience for beginners as well as seasoned developers alike. You’ll end up with a mini-project to show-off on your resume, and with prizes worth 5 lakhs, speaker sessions from industry experts, schwags, and fun in-hack activities, you definitely don’t wanna miss this!
